name: Fade Away (itch) (Jack_h80)
description:
Fade Away!!!

Make your way through the level to make it to the end, but watch out for the obstacles and FADING AWAY!!!! Yes fading away, collect the skulls to restart the fade and make it through the level.

Good Luck!!!!

WARNING!!!!

There is sound in this game so turn down headphones or mute if you don't want to listen :)

Made by Jack and Jack's assistant Atilla
